title: Single-cell RNA-seq reveals hypothalamic cell diversity
abstract: We performed single-cell RNA-seq of mouse hypothalamus to reveal the cell diversity of this region.
overall_design: Hypothalamus of mice (kept in normal condition or food deprivation) were dissected for single-cell RNA-seq through Drop-seq technique.
summary: We performed single-cell RNA-seq of mouse hypothalamus to reveal the cell diversity of this region.
